channel.title: Galkon's Anarchy v1.5 .java files?
channel.description:
Is there any way to get these? I downloaded the client and love it. It corrected a lot of messed up models from a previous client and fire cape textured water... I dont really wanna change clients but is has only the egui.java file.
I was wondering if anyone here posibbly had the class1-class50, and the Client.java files... Or if he even released them. He said it was open source which means editable i do believe but you need java files to edit them.
Also a bit off topic but is there a .class to .java converter?
